mobs.keywords: lizard man neo neo-lizard-man reptilian creature humanoid
mobs.long_desc: A nearly humanoid reptilian creature stands here, watching you coldly.
mobs.desc: It doesn't quite look intelligent, but it is obviously a step higher on the scale than a simple lizard. It watches you coldly, as if you were nothing more to it than a possible meal. There seems to be only a trace of intelligence in this creature.

mobs.long_desc: The Northern Crusher Bile is here with an evil gleam in his eyes.
mobs.desc: Larger than a regular bile, the Crusher Biles are an Elite Force. Bred for a love of violence and given the strength to rip someone's arms off, the Crusher are the most feared of the bile.

mobs.long_desc: The Bile Rot is standing here, ready to tear your head off.
mobs.desc: Standing well over 7 feet tall, this creature was once a bile but a horrible transformation has taken place. Infected with some sort of disease, the Bile Rot has grown to enormous proportions. You can see worms crawling from its eye sockets and there appears to be something moving underneath of its skin.

mobs.long_desc: The crazy old hermit stands here, ready to fight if necessary.
mobs.desc: He's a large fellow, but very old, with a wispy grey beard and equally sparse grey hair. He talks to himself constantly and moves with great deliberation and slowness.

mobs.long_desc: A mysteriously cloaked man rests against his longbow here.
mobs.desc: This cloaked figure is a gracious ranger, looking out for the young but adventurous.  He is tall and sleek, and well built, ready to help if need be.

objects.ground: Someone has left a rusty old blade here.
A pair of grungy old boots has been left here.
A murky potion has been dropped here.

triggers.name: North Swamp Entrance Guard
triggers.commands: if %actor.vnum% == -1 if %actor.level% < 20 return 1 whisper %actor.name% My, my, young adventurer, you are ambitious. whisper %actor.name% It is just a bit too dangerous for you to head further east. wait 1s whisper %actor.name% It is safer to head back the other way. bow %actor.name% else return 0 endif else return 0 endif

rooms.name: The Beginning of the Northern Swamp Road
rooms.description: A gatehouse stands just to the south of here, with the fortress itself rising up behind it, bleak and obviously abandoned. A wide dirt road begins here and runs to the north, with swamps lying to either side.

North.description: You see the Northern Swamp Road.

South.description: You see the Postern Gatehouse of Mystwatch. The gate appears to have been recently destroyed.
